    "longBusinessSummary": "Agribank Securities Corporation provides securities brokerage, securities trading, securities underwriting, securities custody, securities investment advisory, entrusted management of investors' securities trading accounts, and other financial services in Vietnam. The company's products include brokerage and investment consulting, financial services, securities depository, securities custody and preservation services, auction agent, and investor money management services. It also provides business consulting services, such as advisory on going public, additional securities issuance, stock listing, equitization, and state capital divestment; strategic partner search consulting, and M&A consulting; other corporate financial advisory services, as well as agribank bonds; and development facilities. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam. Agribank Securities Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Vietnam Bank for Agriculture and Rural Development.",
